# Simone Livraghi Personal Website

## Project Overview
Personal portfolio website for Simone Livraghi, an AI Systems Engineer & Software Architect based in Milan, Italy. This is a complete, production-ready single-page React application.

## Project Location
**Root Directory**: `~/Repository/websites/simonelivraghi.com/`

