## Key Features Implemented
- ‚úÖ Single page application with smooth scroll navigation
- ‚úÖ All 8 required sections: Home, About, Skills, Experience, Projects, Certifications, Values, Contact
- ‚úÖ Dark/light mode toggle with system preference detection
- ‚úÖ Fully mobile responsive design
- ‚úÖ SEO optimized with meta tags and structured data
- ‚úÖ WCAG 2.1 AA accessible
- ‚úÖ Material Design 3 inspired UI
- ‚úÖ Fast Vite build system

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: React 19 with Vite
- **Styling**: Custom CSS with CSS Variables
- **SEO**: React Helmet Async
- **Font**: Inter (Google Fonts)
- **Icons**: Unicode emojis
- **Theme**: Dark/Light mode with localStorage persistence

